I created a `vext.SoapySDR` package and was able to work-around this error by stubbing `bdist_wheel` so it didn't actually do anything.

```
try:
    from wheel.bdist_wheel import bdist_wheel as _bdist_wheel
    class bdist_wheel(_bdist_wheel):
        def run(self):
            return
except ImportError:
    bdist_wheel = None
```

